snippet.title: ToP Projects Compilation
snippet.description:
TPC is a youtube community/channel providing creative projects based on Arduino/Raspberry-Pi/ESP32 to beginners as well as advanced hobbyists. 

If you think you have a unique project based on Arduino/ Raspberry Pi/ ESP32/ ESP8266 that can help hobbyists and students all over the world then please contact us at:

Email ID: tpcinfo2018@gmail.com
Instagram: tpc_insta
